00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.920
The second way of coordinating activities would be cascaded events.

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:07.470
In state charts the response to an event can be the broadcasting of

00:00:07.470 --> 00:00:12.580
another internal event. Because all states listen for all events, this

00:00:12.580 --> 00:00:16.504
mechanism can be used to communicate between concurrently executing sub-machines

